FBIS4-58538 "drnes087_r_94003" FBIS-NES-94-087 Daily Report 5 May 1994 SOUTH ASIA India Government Monitoring Pakistan's Aircraft Supply Government Monitoring Pakistan's Aircraft Supply BK0505095294 Delhi All India Radio Network in English 0830 GMT 5 May 94 BK0505095294 Delhi All India Radio Network English BFN [Text] The government is taking appropriate steps to counter the situation arising out of threat of the supply of F-16 aircrafts to Pakistan by the United States. In a written reply in the Rajya Sabha today, the minister of state for defense, Mr. Mallikarjun, assured the house that the government is closely monitoring the matter concerning the supply of these aircrafts and steps are being taken to counter it.
